<h1>Visualizations</h1>

<p>Every interactive visualization from the project, in lesson order. Each one was built to make a specific theorem or definition tangible — drag points, move sliders, and step through proofs.</p>

<div class="viz-grid">
  {% for viz in visualizations %}
  <a class="viz-card" href="/visualizations/{{ viz.slug }}/">
    <span class="viz-card-lesson">{{ viz.lesson }}</span>
    <h2>{{ viz.title }}</h2>
    <p>{{ viz.description }}</p>
  </a>
  {% endfor %}
</div>
